The King Of The Degodia Community Across The World His Majesty Wabar Abdille Continued His 21 Day Tour Of The Country With A Visit To Wajir County This Weekend. The King Who Was Hosted By Northern Kenya Leaders Asked The Various Communities Residing In The Northern Region To Unite And Peacefully Co?Exist In The Interest Of Development. The Objective Of The Tour By The King Of The Degodia Who Arrived Last Week On Friday Is To Enhance Peace And Unity Between Neighboring Communities And Countries. Wabar Abdille Is The 12th Wabar In The Leadership Lineage And This Is His First?Time Visit In Kenya To Enhance Peace And Unity.